{"sessionKey":"42nd3rd52b","paragraphs":[{"html":"<a name=\"StartOfColumns\"></a><b><i>The House met at 1:30 p.m.</i></b>","index":"00000","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Deputy Speaker (Doyle Piwniuk):</b>\nGood afternoon, everyone. Please be seated. ","index":"00001","speaker":"Doyle Piwniuk"},{"html":"<b>Mr. Deputy Speaker:</b> Introduction\nof bills? ","index":"00002","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Deputy Speaker:</b> The\nhonourable member for Radisson. The honourable member for Radisson? ","index":"00003","speaker":""},{"html":"����� The honourable member for\nRadisson, do you want to unmute your mic.","index":"00004","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. James Teitsma (Radisson):</b>\nYes. ","index":"00005","speaker":"James Teitsma"},{"html":"<span style=\"display:none\">&nbsp;</span>","index":"00006","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Deputy Speaker:</b> There we go. ","index":"00007","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Teitsma:</b> I'm sorry, Mr.\nDeputy Speaker. A little trouble with the audio, there.","index":"00008","speaker":"James Teitsma"},{"html":"<b>Mr. James</b><b>�<a name=\"_Toc69889063\">Teitsma</a></b><b>�(Chairperson):</b> I wish to present\nthe seventh report of the Standing Committee on Social and Economic\nDevelopment.� ","index":"00009","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Clerk (Ms. Patricia Chaychuk):</b>\nYour Standing Committee on Social and Economic Development� ","index":"00010","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>An Honourable Member:</b> Dispense. ","index":"00011","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Deputy Speaker:</b> Dispense. ","index":"00012","speaker":""},{"html":"<i>Your Standing Committee on Social and\nEconomic Development presents the following as its Seventh Report.</i>","index":"00013","speaker":""},{"html":"<b><i>Meetings</i></b>","index":"00014","speaker":""},{"html":"<i>Your Committee met on April 19, 2021\nat 6:00 p.m. in Room 255 of the Legislative Building.</i>","index":"00015","speaker":""},{"html":"<b><i>Matters under Consideration</i></b>","index":"00016","spe